docblock.long-description:
It is possible but not recomended to use constructor for
obtaining an instance of HttpRequest, use {@see HttpRequest::build($url)}
instead.

If you do not use Composer, you can
add this in the begining of your <code>__autoload</code> chain f.ex.
<br>
<pre><code>
function __autoload($className) {
&nbsp;&nbsp;if (httpClientAutoLoad($className)) {
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return;
&nbsp;&nbsp;}
&nbsp;&nbsp;//your code here
}
</code></pre>
